tak ada yang peduli.

1169
01:26:23,251 --> 01:26:24,334
Pulanglah.

1170
01:26:36,959 --> 01:26:38,126
Record American.

1171
01:26:40,584 --> 01:26:42,584
UNTUK SAUDARIKU SALLY

